Dvoyre un Perl.

00:25:14.644 --> 00:25:16.477
hobn zey gevoynt bay undz.

00:25:16.686 --> 00:25:19.321
un dernokh dem, s'hot zikh geendikt,

00:25:19.321 --> 00:25:20.780
m'hot undz bafrayt,

00:25:22.660 --> 00:25:24.459
iz der bruder,

00:25:24.634 --> 00:25:27.851
der Avrom, mit der shvester, mit der klenerer,

00:25:28.532 --> 00:25:31.394
avekgeforn keyn, Besarabye,

00:25:32.143 --> 00:25:36.898
un di eltere shvester hot khasene gehat farn rebe fun Tshetshelnik.

00:25:39.028 --> 00:25:40.811
VOT ot o dos gedenk ikh.

00:25:41.897 --> 00:25:43.528
nu, ⟨un⟩ vayter, fregt.

00:25:42.994 --> 00:25:44.591
nu, geyt men tsurik,

00:25:44.901 --> 00:25:48.979
ir zent geven in di shtub, s'hobn gevoynt a sakh mentshn tsuzamen.

00:25:48.681 --> 00:25:49.434
 ye.

00:25:49.558 --> 00:25:55.682
vi iz azoy gegangen yedn tog? vos hot men gegesn? vos hot men, vos hot men, di mentshn, vos hobn zey getun a gantsn tog?

00:25:55.313 --> 00:25:57.956
di, bay undz hobn gevoynt,

00:25:57.962 --> 00:25:59.390
fun,

00:26:00.139 --> 00:26:01.871
Strozhinits,

00:26:03.126 --> 00:26:04.588
fun Zhadeve...

00:26:06.552 --> 00:26:10.359
VOT ⟨epe-⟩ nokh fun Bukovine. ikh gedenk nit.

00:26:10.686 --> 00:26:14.240
ikh gedenk nor az zey hobn gehat LEYes,

00:26:15.090 --> 00:26:17.480
un zey flegn zikh aroysganvenen,

00:26:17.858 --> 00:26:19.472
emetser fun zey,

00:26:19.528 --> 00:26:21.969
un zey flegn geyn un epes koyfn.

00:26:24.000 --> 00:26:26.120
hobn zey gelebt. un mir,

00:26:26.633 --> 00:26:29.698
hot men undz bald ongehoybn traybn in kolkhoz arayn,

00:26:30.531 --> 00:26:32.803
az me zol SOBIRAen dem UROZHAY.

00:26:34.463 --> 00:26:38.237
dos iz geven shoyn avgust khoydesh, KONETS AVGUSTA,

00:26:39.154 --> 00:26:41.156
un S- onheyb SENTYABR'.

00:26:42.782 --> 00:26:44.851
iz hot men undz gezogt, di goyim,

00:26:45.972 --> 00:26:48.818
"vos, bay vos ir arbet,

00:26:49.060 --> 00:26:52.631
STARAet zikh, ir zolt zikh nemen mit zikh aheym tsu bislekh."

00:26:53.312 --> 00:26:57.052
un zey flegn undz helfn, az mir zoln durkhgeyn.

00:26:57.852 --> 00:27:05.574
hot men gegrobn kartofl, hobn mir oykhet UNK genemen. dos bin ikh gegan, un der bruder, un der foter mayner.

00:27:06.272 --> 00:27:08.139
gedenk ikh, s'ershte mol,

00:27:08.685 --> 00:27:12.543
⟨iz⟩, zenen mir gegan, mir zenen nisht geven tsugevoynt tsu derinen.

00:27:13.005 --> 00:27:14.636
hot men undz genemen

00:27:14.828 --> 00:27:20.272
in a shtub arayn arbetn, me zol bay ir, dem gortn, UBIRAen.

00:27:20.987 --> 00:27:23.085
geven di PANI ⟨LYUBАSHEVSKе⟩.

00:27:23.085 --> 00:27:25.318
oyf der ⟨KOLOSIIVKe⟩ hot zi gevoynt.

00:27:26.269 --> 00:27:28.018
hot zi undz gehodevet.

00:27:29.475 --> 00:27:30.788
etlekhe teg

00:27:30.788 --> 00:27:35.409
hobn mir bay ir gegesn, gehodevet hot zi undz, un zi fleg undz nokh gibn aheym epes.

00:27:36.360 --> 00:27:38.126
un dernokh, in kolkhoz,

00:27:38.166 --> 00:27:39.408
zog ikh zikh aykh,

00:27:39.567 --> 00:27:40.972
mir hobn gearbet

00:27:40.972 --> 00:27:42.648
un zi fleg undz,

00:27:43.347 --> 00:27:46.041
oykhet flegn mir brengen mit zikh.

00:27:46.941 --> 00:27:48.150
un dernokh...

00:27:48.325 --> 00:27:53.955
dos iz shoyn geven, mir hobn nit gevust az zey, ⟨a- f-⟩ farshraybn undz di TRUDODNI,

00:27:55.176 --> 00:27:59.164
azoy vi ⟨f- m-⟩ se fleg zayn in di kolkhozn, az m'hot gearbet,

00:27:59.164 --> 00:28:00.182
di goyim,

00:28:00.576 --> 00:28:02.645
fleg ⟨me⟩n di TRUDODNI shraybn,

00:28:02.922 --> 00:28:04.789
nu, vifl eyner hot fardint,

00:28:05.082 --> 00:28:05.936
vi azoy.

00:28:06.145 --> 00:28:07.776
hobn zey undz geshribn.

00:28:08.710 --> 00:28:14.391
mir hobn dos zikh nit forgeshtelt. mir hobn getrakht, mir hobn opgearbet vos m'hot undz getribn un shoyn, farfaln.

00:28:15.696 --> 00:28:16.669
in

00:28:16.675 --> 00:28:17.710
osyen

00:28:17.710 --> 00:28:20.398
zenen mir ale farshlaft gevorn oyf tif.

00:28:22.902 --> 00:28:23.985
VSЁ.
